ed.\",\n  \"deterministic_setup\": [],\n  \"agent_guidance\": \"For native runtime tests of Vert.x Web Client 5.0.1 on JDK 25, configure the native test runtime with system properties `-Dsun.misc.unsafe.memory.access=allow` and `-Dio.netty.tryReflectionSetAccessible=true`. Meaningful coverage should use an in-process Vert.x `HttpServer` rather than external services; no Docker service is required.\",\n  \"risks\": [\n    \"The system properties address the known Netty 4.2.x unsafe/reflection runtime requirement, but local Gradle/native-image verification remains authoritative for any additional GraalVM metadata regression.\",\n    \"Optional Vert.x Web Client integrations such as OAuth2 are declared optional and should not be added unless tests intentionally cover those APIs.\"\n  ]\n}", "textSignature": "{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_062a2091a748c292016a40da9280b481978636cb7e7ef6ea55\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "oca/gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 672, "output": 620, "cacheRead": 20992, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 22284, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "stop", "timestamp": 1782635148533, "responseId": "resp_062a2091a748c292016a40da8d24dc81978ff7d782aa36c0c1"}, "toolResults": []}
